These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: billiard, whist, bridge
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
3. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Game   | bridge | whist | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
City: venice, boston, paris
1. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | venice | paris | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, snowmobile
1. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Transport   | roller | subway | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, brown, turquise
1. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Color   | blue | turquise | brown |

