.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Birthday   | january | august | october |

